{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"DogFoodAndFun Approval API","description":"Localhost-only sidecar for parallel web/Telegram approvals.","version":"0.2.0"},"paths":{"/api/v1/campaigns":{"get":{"tags":["campaigns"],"summary":"List Campaigns","description":"Return one summary per folder under campaigns_dir that has a config.\n\nFolders without ``campaign_config.json`` are silently skipped — the\nUI only renders runnable campaigns. Invalid configs are also skipped\n(logged at WARN) so a single broken JSON file can't 500 the list.","operationId":"list_campaigns_api_v1_campaigns_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CampaignListResponse"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/campaigns/{name}":{"get":{"tags":["campaigns"],"summary":"Get Campaign","description":"Return full detail (summary + history) for a single campaign.","operationId":"get_campaign_api_v1_campaigns__name__get","parameters":[{"name":"name","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","pattern":"^[a-z0-9][a-z0-9_-]*$","title":"Name"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CampaignDetail"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/campaigns/{name}/publish":{"post":{"tags":["campaigns"],"summary":"Publish Campaign","description":"Spawn ``scripts.publish_campaign`` as a detached subprocess.\n\nFire-and-forget by design: the publisher writes to ``state.json`` and\nthe frontend polls ``GET /campaigns``. Lock conflicts surface there\nas ``last_status=\"error\"`` on the next poll, identical to the cron\npath. Returns immediately with the spawned PID.","operationId":"publish_campaign_api_v1_campaigns__name__publish_post","parameters":[{"name":"name","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","pattern":"^[a-z0-9][a-z0-9_-]*$","t